data.description: Wonderful property includes home with 3 bedrooms, an office, 3 bathrooms, and is 2224 SF with a double car attached garage. There is a large 1728 SF 3 bay shop with two 14' doors plus a detached single car garage, all on a 1.27 acre lot. Centrally located in a nice neighborhood. This home features beautiful tongue and groove wood ceilings and nice finishes and plenty of room for a large family or entertaining. Gorgeous laminate flooring, granite counters thru out, and a large kitchen with a pantry. Home has a heat pump with whole house cooling. The grounds are fenced and landscaped with underground sprinklers and an asphalt driveway. This is a wonderful property!!!!!
